import Vue from 'vue'
import Vuex from 'vuex'
import { vuex as storeUsuario } from '@/Usuario'
import { vuex as storeVistante } from '@/Visitante'

const debug = process.env.NODE_ENV !== 'production'
Vue.use(Vuex)
export default new Vuex.Store({
  modules: { ...storeUsuario, ...storeVistante },
  strict: debug
})
